〈榮耀極限〉由Lady Gaga、[[Fernando_Garibay|Fernando Garibay]]和DJ White Shadow合写，由Gaga和Garibay共同制作。<ref name="ET">{{cite web|url=http://music-mix.ew.com/2011/05/09/lady-gaga-the-edge-of-glory-new-single/|title=Lady Gaga releases new single 'The Edge of Glory': Listen here|first=Christian|last=Blauvelt|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|publisher=[[Time,_Inc.|Time, Inc.]]|date=2011-05-09|accessdate=2011-05-09|archive-date=2011-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110510134311/http://music-mix.ew.com/2011/05/09/lady-gaga-the-edge-of-glory-new-single/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 歌曲内容最初在2011年一月发布，当时Gaga在她的[[Twitter|Twitter]]账号上面发布了歌词的一部分。<ref name="MTV">{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1663469/lady-gaga-edge-of-glory.jhtml|title=Lady Gaga Teases 'The Edge Of Glory' Release On Monday|first=Jocelyn|last=Vena|publisher=MTV. MTV Networks|date=2011-05-05|accessdate=2011-05-09|archive-date=2012-07-30|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69Y6VRInv?url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1663469/lady-gaga-edge-of-glory.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref> DJ White Shadow透露在回到欧洲的Monster Ball表演之前，Gaga抽出了几天去陪她患病的祖父。在他去世后，Gaga告诉他自己写了一首有关她祖父之死的歌曲，并称这首歌强调了这件事对她的影响。<ref name="ins">{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1663791/lady-gaga-edge-of-glory.jhtml|title=Lady Gaga's 'Edge Of Glory' Inspired By Late Grandfather|first=Jocelyn|last=Vena|publisher=MTV. MTV Networks|date=2011-05-13|accessdate=2011-05-13|archive-date=2011-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111114101456/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1663791/lady-gaga-edge-of-glory.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

